    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为收银系统画一个状态图，从系统启动开始，先进入空闲状态，等开始新账单再进入扫描商品。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "Idle",
        "ScanningItems"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，起点到Idle是系统启动，Idle到扫描状态是开始新账单。那扫描过程中如果顾客想加更多商品，这个循环怎么处理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ScanningItems",
        "Add More Items"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "扫描状态要有个自循环，标注\"Add More Items\"。另外扫描时还要显示实时计算总额、验证商品、检查库存，这些我打算用注释框放在扫描状态右边。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ScanningItems",
        "Updates running total",
        "Validates product",
        "Checks inventory"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，已添加扫描状态的自循环和右侧注释。扫描完成后应该进入计算总额状态对吧？还有取消交易的情况。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ScanningItems",
        "CalculatingTotal",
        "Idle",
        "Cancel Transaction"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，扫描完成到计算总额，取消的话直接回空闲状态。计算总额之后，确认总额就进入支付，如果想改商品还能退回扫描状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CalculatingTotal",
        "ProcessingPayment",
        "ScanningItems",
        "Total Confirmed",
        "Modify Items"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "支付状态需要支持哪些方式？另外支付失败的处理逻辑是？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ProcessingPayment"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "支付方式在注释里列出现金、刷卡、数字支付三种。支付成功去打印小票，失败就返回重新计算总额。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ProcessingPayment",
        "PrintingReceipt",
        "CalculatingTotal",
        "Cash",
